<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَمُضَارِعٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَمُطَلِّقَةٍ، بِكَسْرِ اللَّامِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- أَنْتِ عَلَيَّ حَرَامٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> أَوْ:</span> كَظَهْرِ أُمِّي.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> أَوْ:</span> مَا أَحَلَّ اللهُ عَلَيَّ حَرَامٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَهُوَ ظِهَارٌ، وَلَو نَوَى طَلَاقاً.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ قَالَ:</span> كَالمَيْتَةِ أَوِ الدَّمِ:<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَقَعَ مَا نَوَاهُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَعَ عَدَمِ نِيَّةٍ:</span> ظِهَارٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ قَالَ:</span> حَلَفْتُ بِالطَّلَاقِ،<span class="c5"> وَكَذَبَ:</span> دُيِّنَ، وَلَزِمَهُ حُكْماً.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَمْلِكُ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> حُرٌّ وَمُبَعَّضٌ:</span> ثَلَاثَ تَطْلِيقَاتٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَعَبْدٌ:</span> اثْنَتَيْنِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- وَيَصِحُّ اسْتِثْنَاءُ النِّصْفِ فَأَقَلَّ مِنْ طَلَقَاتٍ، وَمُطَلَّقَاتٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>